conveying the senses of ‘out of’,
‘away from’, ‘without’, ‘free from’,
and may be frequently expressed
by ‘less’, ‘un’, used with the noun;
see the compounds given below;
see {#nis#} and <ab>cf.</ab> {#a#} also.

